        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer71899350" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6255910130456933722">4 ½ stars – Contemporary Romance/Romantic Suspense<br/><br/>Gray is a really hot alpha hero, but his treatment of the heroine throughout most of the book pissed me off. Although, his whole macho, lion hear me roar thing was admittedly pretty sexy and hard to resist at times. And OMG, the notorious porch scene is scorch your fingertips, drink some ice water, YOWZA, smokin&apos; hot and makes this a definite keeper!! It&apos;s another great LH read, but I wish Gray had done a little bit more groveling to Faith and an</span>
  <span id="freeText6255910130456933722" style="display:none">4 ½ stars – Contemporary Romance/Romantic Suspense<br /><br />Gray is a really hot alpha hero, but his treatment of the heroine throughout most of the book pissed me off. Although, his whole macho, lion hear me roar thing was admittedly pretty sexy and hard to resist at times. And OMG, the notorious porch scene is scorch your fingertips, drink some ice water, YOWZA, smokin' hot and makes this a definite keeper!! It's another great LH read, but I wish Gray had done a little bit more groveling to Faith and an epilogue would have been golden! 4 ½ stars! </span>
